https://github.com/llir/llvm/issues/31

- [ ] `half`: 16-bit floating point type
	- [ ] encode
	- [ ] decode
- [ ] `float`: 32-bit floating point type
	- [x] encode: https://golang.org/pkg/math/#Float32bits
	- [x] decode: https://golang.org/pkg/math/#Float32frombits
- [ ] `double`: 64-bit floating point type
	- [x] encode: https://golang.org/pkg/math/#Float64bits
	- [x] decode: https://golang.org/pkg/math/#Float64frombits
- [ ] `fp128`: 128-bit floating point type (112-bit mantissa)
	- [ ] encode
	- [ ] decode
- [ ] `x86_fp80`: 80-bit floating point type (x87)
	- [ ] encode
	- [ ] decode
- [ ] `ppc_fp128`: 128-bit floating point type (two 64-bits, PowerPC)
	- [ ] encode
	- [ ] decode
